Doc: The different options for specifying the attributes of a coal quality measure as a decimal value.

Source.Contents:
/#
   The different options for specifying the attributes of a coal quality measure as a decimal value.
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.CoalAttributeDecimal {
  # The actual content of the quality characteristics of the Coal Product Shipment expected by the Buyer.
  standardContent : decimal?

  # The actual limits of the quality characteristics of the Coal Product above or below which the Buyer may reject a Shipment.
  rejectionLimit : decimal?

}

standardContent.Doc: The actual content of the quality characteristics of the Coal Product Shipment expected by the Buyer.
standardContent.Name: standardContent

rejectionLimit.Doc: The actual limits of the quality characteristics of the Coal Product above or below which the Buyer may reject a Shipment.
rejectionLimit.Name: rejectionLimit
